POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderName": "",
  "senderEmail": "",
  "subject": "",
  "messageBody": ""
}

### Obtener mensajes de contacto
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/messages
Accept: application/json

